 <h2><a href="http://mymhgift.org/" target="">About Mission Hospital</a></h2>
 <p>Mission Hospital was founded in Mission Viejo in 1971 and has continued to develop new programs and services to meet the ever changing needs of the community. In 1993, Mission Hospital partnered with CHOC Children?s to provide pediatric services and a year later, became a member of the St. Joseph Health network of care. In 2009, Mission Hospital expanded its geographic footprint to include south Orange County?s coast line by acquiring Mission Hospital Laguna Beach.</p>
