 <section class="right cdd-content cdd-doc-content" original-class="right cdd-content cdd-doc-content" icobalt="CobaltControls.Controls.DisplayItem" id="CDDoctorCTA" name="CDDoctorCTA"><p><strong>Mission Hospital</strong> has an award-winning staff that is leading the way in medical ingenuity. Our accomplishments have led to such awards as the Outstanding Achievement Award for the Commission on Cancer in 2008 ? causing us to be one of 66 hospitals in the entire nation to be honored. Combining care for the mind, body and spirit, we take a unique approach to every individual patient.</p>
